songs.title: Eh, Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)

But my friends keepa' tellin' me that something’s wrong
Then I met someone
And eh

Eh-eh, eh-eh

Eh-eh, eh-eh

Eh-eh, eh-eh

Eh-eh, hey-eh-ey

And eh

Eh-eh, hey-eh-ey (ooh, yeah)

Eh-eh, hey
